Log.Item2:
*sigh* If only my life wasn't so busy… Maybe I could convince him…
Oh! Sorry, good evening, dear bartender. I was a bit lost in my thoughts.
Would you be so kind as to get me a sweet drink, like a Spring Bee? Maybe that will distract me from my career…I'm an actress, you see.

Posters.name: Poster 5
Posters.description: Ernest has gifted you this poster, which allegedly comes from Turin, Italy. Its vibrant colors will give you more energy during your shift, but they might also attract unwanted attention...

Posters.name: Asti Cinzano
Posters.description: This intriguing poster is heavily inspired by Baroque paintings, and perhaps reminds us that alcoholic beverages have always been a part of human society.
